    </div>

    <div class="bento-grid">
      <a class="bento-card bento-feature" href="/checkout/">
        <div class="bento-num">01</div>
        <div class="bento-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="bento-title">Overall winner: theStacc</h3>
        <h4 class="bento-sub">The best <span class="accent">content automation tool for HVAC</span> in 2026 — 30 articles + 30 GBP posts, handles seasonal targeting automatically.</h4>
        <p class="bento-desc">Publishes 30 HVAC blog articles monthly covering seasonal demand: AC content in spring/summer, heating content in fall/winter. Plus 30 GBP posts monthly. The only tool on this list that creates content instead of just tracking it.</p>
        <ul class="bento-list">
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>30 HVAC blog articles per month — seasonal targeting built in</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>30 GBP posts monthly — consistent activity signals to Google</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Bundle discount: ~$126/mo for blog + local</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>$1 trial · No contract · Cancel anytime</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="bento-mock">
          <div class="bento-mock-bar">
            <div class="bento-mock-meta">THESTACC · #1 OVERALL · $99/MO BLOG</div>
            <span class="bento-mock-pulse"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-mock-title">~$3.30 per article · seasonal HVAC content on autopilot</div>
