              <p>SEO agencies charge $1,000–5,000/month. theStacc delivers more content output at $99–126/month.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS ROW -->
  <section>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">10<span class="accent"></span></div><div class="stat-label">Tools tested for HVAC SEO</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">300<span class="accent">%</span></div><div class="stat-label">Seasonal search swing · summer vs. winter HVAC</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">30<span class="accent"></span></div><div class="stat-label">Articles/month from theStacc — seasonal targeting included</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">$126<span class="accent">/mo</span></div><div class="stat-label">theStacc bundle vs. $1,000–5,000 for agencies</div></div>
