          <a href="/checkout/" class="btn btn-primary"><span>Start the $1 trial <span class="arrow">→</span></span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-grid" id="service-2" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#2 · FREE</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Google Business Profile — Best free local listing for HVAC companies</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">The foundation every HVAC company must claim and optimize before spending on any other tool.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">GBP is free and essential for local search visibility. Service area definition by city, county, or radius. Photo and video uploads. Service menu listing. Review collection and response. Insights dashboard. The limitation is that everything is manual — no automation, no scheduling, no content suggestions built in.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Completely free — all features included</h4><p>Claim, verify, and fully complete your GBP before spending a dollar on any other tool.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Service area definition by city, county, or radius</h4><p>Critical for HVAC companies covering wide geographic areas rather than a single storefront.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: manual everything — no automation</h4><p>Every post, photo, and update is manual. Pair with theStacc to automate GBP posting at scale.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-grid" id="service-3" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#3 · $39–59/MO PER LOCATION</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">BrightLocal — Best local SEO tracking suite for HVAC</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For HVAC companies who want to see exactly where they rank across their full service territory.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">BrightLocal's geo-grid rank tracking shows your Maps ranking across your service area — revealing which cities you dominate and which ones you're invisible in. Citation auditing across 50+ HVAC directories. GBP audit with optimization scoring. Review monitoring across Google, Yelp, and Facebook. White-label reporting for franchise owners. The best tracking suite for HVAC at this price.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Geo-grid rank tracking across full service territory</h4><p>See your Maps ranking at every point in your coverage zone. Essential for HVAC companies serving 20–50+ miles.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Citation auditing across 50+ HVAC directories</h4><p>Catches NAP inconsistencies across Angi, HomeAdvisor, BBB, and other contractor directories.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: no content creation or seasonal adjustment</h4><p>BrightLocal measures the problem. Pair it with theStacc to actually fix it through seasonal content.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-grid" id="service-4" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#4 · $19–69/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Localo — Best budget GBP optimizer for HVAC</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For HVAC companies that want specific GBP improvement recommendations at the lowest price point.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Localo audits your GBP, scores it, and provides specific recommendations: missing categories, attribute gaps, competitor differences, photo opportunities. Includes post templates and local keyword rank tracking. The limitation is that it recommends without executing — you still have to make the changes yourself. Good for a first-month audit to identify quick wins.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>AI-driven GBP audit with optimization scoring</h4><p>Category and attribute recommendations specific to HVAC businesses, with competitor comparison.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Local keyword rank tracking included</h4><p>Track "AC repair near me" and core HVAC service keywords alongside the GBP audit.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: advisory only — no auto-posting</h4><p>Recommends but doesn't execute. You still have to write and post GBP updates manually after getting the recommendations.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-grid" id="service-5" style="margin-top: 48px;">
