        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Local Falcon shows your Maps ranking on a geographic grid. You can see your position at every point across your 30-mile service area — down to individual neighborhoods. Seasonal keyword tracking capability. Competitor ranking comparison at the same grid points. AI-driven local SEO audit with recommendations. It's a tracking-only tool, but the visualization is the most useful in the category for HVAC's wide-area coverage challenge.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Geographic grid reveals ranking gaps across the full service zone</h4><p>Shows which neighborhoods you're invisible in — information you can't get from standard rank tracking.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Seasonal keyword tracking capability</h4><p>Track "AC repair" in summer, "furnace replacement" in fall — different keywords for different times of year.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: tracking only — no content or optimization</h4><p>Local Falcon shows you the gap; theStacc fills it. They complement each other well at a combined $124/month.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-grid" id="service-6" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#6 · $52/MO + LOCAL ADD-ONS</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">SE Ranking — Best full SEO suite for HVAC companies</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For HVAC companies with in-house marketing who want keyword research, site audits, and competitor analysis in one platform.</p>
