          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Two factors make HVAC SEO distinct: seasonal demand swings (AC searches spike in summer, heating in winter) and wide service areas (20–50+ miles). Your content strategy needs to match seasonal cycles, and your rank tracking needs to cover your full geographic service zone — not just your office zip code.</div>
